## TTL-first documentation strategy. This KB replaces multiple markdown docs:
## KB_VS_MARKDOWN.md, LOCAL_HOME_FOLDER.md, PROV_O_ALIGNMENT.md,
## DEPENDENCIES.md, MOBILE_LOCAL_SERVER.md, MOBILE_CAPTURE.md,
## SECURITY.md (expanded), STYLE_GUIDE.md (summary).
